Class BlockProtConfig

java.lang.Object
de.dei0.blockprot.bukkit.config.BlockProtConfig
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultConfig
public abstract class BlockProtConfig extends Object
Represents a basic YAML configuration file with some basic utility functions for manipulating common config data.

  • Method Details

    • listContainsIgnoreCase

      protected boolean listContainsIgnoreCase(@NotNull @NotNull List<String> list, @NotNull @NotNull String query)
      Checks whether or not the given list contains the query String. It checks each item using String.equalsIgnoreCase(String).
      Parameters:
      list - The list of strings to check.
      query - The string to compare to.
      Returns:
      True, if any item of list qualifies for String.equalsIgnoreCase(String) with query.

    • loadEnumValuesByName

      @NotNull protected <T extends Enum<?>> @NotNull Set<T> loadEnumValuesByName(@NotNull T[] enumValues, @NotNull @NotNull ArrayList<String> names)
      Filter a list of enum values by a list of names. The enum values are filtered by names.
      Type Parameters:
      T - The enum class.
      Parameters:
      enumValues - The list of enum values we want to filter.
      names - The list strings we want to filter by. Warning: This list will be modified.
      Returns:
      A set of all <T> enum values that we found.
